# Approval Workflow

## Roles
- Owner: canon authority
- Producer: release strategy, sponsor readiness, and launch timing
- Editor: story, host framing, and public copy
- Legal reviewer: release, music, clip, and ad compliance review
- Publicist: press and website approval

## Rules
- Locked fields require owner approval to change
- Approved public fields may be exported to site and press pages
- Draft fields stay internal unless explicitly approved
